0:02:27.680,0:02:28.270
Your Majesty.

0:02:30.080,0:02:30.760
Your Majesty.

0:02:31.800,0:02:35.333
Noble Consort Lumière has been waiting inside for some time.

0:02:39.080,0:02:41.243
Call for Noble Prince Guo to wait here.

0:02:42.800,0:02:45.779
He must not enter until I summon him.

0:02:45.960,0:02:46.700
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:02:56.200,0:02:57.379
Your Majesty has returned.

0:03:08.760,0:03:09.775
Why does Your Majesty...

0:03:10.357,0:03:12.443
look at me like that?

0:03:13.600,0:03:15.040
When did it begin?

0:03:20.766,0:03:24.946
Pardon my slow-wittedness.
I don't know what Your Majesty refers to.

0:03:30.280,0:03:32.000
I've doted on you all these years.

0:03:33.176,0:03:34.760
But in this moment,

0:03:35.480,0:03:38.329
I truly resent your face.

0:03:39.800,0:03:45.538
I was reminded today of Emperor Yuan, who 
married off his concubine Zhaojun to the west.

0:03:46.800,0:03:48.009
Galdan said it?

0:03:49.160,0:03:51.047
Galdan requested an audience with me.

0:03:51.200,0:03:53.396
He asked for a marriage alliance - to marry you.

0:03:57.320,0:04:00.640
How did you catch his eye?

0:04:02.320,0:04:04.202
I'm Your Majesty's concubine.

0:04:04.680,0:04:06.600
How can I abase myself in a marriage alliance?

0:04:06.600,0:04:07.760
Galdan is truly absurd!

0:04:07.760,0:04:09.499
Of course I know he is.

0:04:10.320,0:04:12.694
I said as much to him, to silence him.

0:04:13.040,0:04:17.049
But he cited the precedent of Emperor Yuan of Han,
and compared you to Zhaojun.

0:04:17.049,0:04:18.779
He asked me to relinquish my love.

0:04:21.120,0:04:23.364
Your face is alluring to me,

0:04:23.668,0:04:26.166
and so it can also allure others.

0:04:26.360,0:04:28.520
I shouldn't have allowed you to meet him.

0:04:28.520,0:04:32.346
Sending Zhaojun beyond the frontier
led to lifelong aching for Emperor Yuan.

0:04:33.960,0:04:35.927
I am Your Majesty's concubine.

0:04:36.640,0:04:38.121
If this happens,

0:04:38.800,0:04:42.928
our children will hang their heads in shame
for the rest of their lives.

0:04:43.240,0:04:46.493
He told me he doesn't care about any of these things.

0:04:47.200,0:04:50.207
He'll do whatever is required to obtain what he likes -

0:04:50.549,0:04:52.160
let alone his desire for you!

0:04:56.000,0:04:58.440
If I'm the cause of Galdan's evil desires,

0:04:58.520,0:05:01.238
I'd rather destroy my looks to save my face.

0:05:03.320,0:05:06.476
It's not only a matter of face.

0:05:07.680,0:05:11.734
Although the plague has won the Great Qing
some time to defend against the Dzungars,

0:05:12.480,0:05:15.880
there's no guarantee that they won't find a cure.

0:05:16.920,0:05:21.503
Moreover, these continuous wars have
greatly depleted the Great Qing's strength.

0:05:22.120,0:05:23.880
I've consulted the Ministry of Revenue.

0:05:23.920,0:05:29.600
Even if we garner all our supplies,
they will support the army for only three to five months.

0:05:31.320,0:05:33.724
Continuing in this deadlock

0:05:33.724,0:05:37.560
will do us "no good but a hundred harms."

0:05:37.800,0:05:39.710
Galdan told me unequivocally

0:05:41.240,0:05:44.350
that as long as I approve you becoming his Consort,

0:05:45.280,0:05:47.622
and give him the remedy for the plague,

0:05:49.680,0:05:52.640
he will wholly recall the Dzungar army.

0:05:53.520,0:05:54.880
And every year from now on,

0:05:54.920,0:05:58.478
they'll take only a hundred thousand silver taels
and food supplies for three thousand troops,

0:05:59.200,0:06:01.920
and will never again cause
the Great Qing's beacon towers to be lit.

0:06:10.160,0:06:11.840
Now I understand, Your Majesty.

0:06:13.680,0:06:15.538
I hold the position of Noble Consort

0:06:16.360,0:06:18.617
and have been favored by Your Majesty for years.

0:06:20.600,0:06:23.200
The time has come to repay Your Majesty's heavenly grace.

0:06:24.960,0:06:27.521
I dare not selfishly cherish my own being.

0:06:28.200,0:06:29.760
I will abide by Your Majesty's wishes.

0:06:31.720,0:06:33.891
I'm the ruler of a nation.

0:06:35.440,0:06:36.534
But this...

0:06:41.240,0:06:43.840
this is for you to decide.

0:06:46.560,0:06:49.807
I dare not forget Your Majesty's grace.

0:06:53.720,0:06:55.360
- Your Noble Highness, please reconsider!
- Your Lordship! Your Lordship!

0:06:55.360,0:06:56.489
It can't be this way!

0:06:57.120,0:06:59.560
Even though Your Noble Highness can set your own well-being aside,

0:06:59.560,0:07:02.240
Your Majesty's reputation for justice will be questioned.

0:07:02.560,0:07:05.760
Your Lordship, His Majesty has not summoned you.

0:07:05.760,0:07:07.124
You cannot enter like this.

0:07:07.360,0:07:08.336
Su Peisheng.

0:07:09.400,0:07:12.214
Let Noble Prince Guo finish, or he'll feel disregarded.

0:07:12.600,0:07:14.189
Your Lordship is overthinking.

0:07:15.080,0:07:16.510
This is my own volition.

0:07:16.800,0:07:18.560
His Majesty hasn't forced me.

0:07:19.047,0:07:21.560
Surely Your Highness doesn't want to
create difficulties for His Majesty.

0:07:21.560,0:07:23.360
If Your Highness enters into this marriage alliance,

0:07:23.360,0:07:25.120
His Majesty will be like Emperor Yuan,

0:07:25.120,0:07:26.713
"the laughingstock of posterity."

0:07:26.713,0:07:29.258
Then how shall I respond to Galdan?

0:07:29.600,0:07:33.696
Your Majesty, Noble Consort Lumière has a
distinguished status as the mother of three children.

0:07:34.000,0:07:36.040
If Her Highness is sent off to a marriage alliance,

0:07:36.040,0:07:38.909
what will Your Majesty tell the Princes and Princesses

0:07:39.200,0:07:40.790
when they ask about their mother?

0:07:42.200,0:07:43.400
Also,

0:07:43.480,0:07:45.226
The Dzungar Khanate is thousands of miles away.

0:07:45.560,0:07:48.000
When Your Majesty misses Noble Consort Lumière in the future,

0:07:48.000,0:07:49.798
you might not be able to see her again.

0:07:50.040,0:07:51.600
Your Majesty adores Her Noble Highness,

0:07:51.600,0:07:54.240
and surely doesn't want her to suffer 
a life spent pacifying the frontier tribes.

0:07:54.440,0:07:56.282
If the Dzungars want a marriage alliance,

0:07:56.282,0:07:59.680
what if Your Majesty seeks someone else
 with talent and beauty to marry Galdan?

0:08:00.000,0:08:03.600
This will protect Her Noble Highness,
and also save face for Galdan.

0:08:03.680,0:08:05.160
You know that

0:08:05.160,0:08:08.780
the devotion of one's heart is extremely
 difficult to change.

0:08:10.320,0:08:12.560
Since he dared to ask for Noble Consort Lumière,

0:08:13.216,0:08:15.308
he must have his heart set on her.

0:08:16.160,0:08:17.440
Do you think

0:08:17.766,0:08:22.240
sending someone else will satisfy Galdan
 enough to back down?

0:08:23.240,0:08:25.680
Your service is not needed here. You may go now.

0:08:25.680,0:08:26.538
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:08:30.400,0:08:33.470
Whether it is Noble Consort Lumière or someone else,

0:08:33.696,0:08:36.228
this is sacrificing a woman's life to protect our homeland.

0:08:36.400,0:08:37.693
What difference does it make?

0:08:38.440,0:08:40.880
If the Dzungars use this as a precedent

0:08:40.880,0:08:43.042
and request a marriage alliance every year,

0:08:43.042,0:08:45.120
won't all women under Heaven be persecuted?

0:08:46.080,0:08:48.640
Where is the dignity of the Great Qing?

0:08:49.400,0:08:51.588
I don't think it is a proper decision, Your Majesty.

0:08:52.877,0:08:56.106
I was blindsided,

0:08:56.840,0:09:00.772
not even noticing when Noble Consort Lumière
caught Galdan's eye.

0:09:01.320,0:09:04.350
Now, I am already deep in this dilemma
 and have lost all dignity.

0:09:04.600,0:09:07.320
Your Majesty, it's not that we can't defeat the Dzungars!

0:09:07.400,0:09:09.184
Do you think I can ...

0:09:09.412,0:09:12.091
bear to give away Noble Consort Lumière?

0:09:15.080,0:09:16.734
It's not that we cannot fight,

0:09:18.560,0:09:20.899
but we cannot be fighting wars like this forever.

0:09:22.080,0:09:23.520
In the current situation,

0:09:23.760,0:09:26.988
how many capable generals do you think we still have?

0:09:32.680,0:09:36.563
The most foolish tactic in the Han Dynasty's history
was the marriage alliance.

0:09:37.040,0:09:38.863
If Your Majesty doesn't despise my incompetence,

0:09:40.240,0:09:42.000
I will lead troops to the frontier

0:09:42.000,0:09:43.937
and not return until the Dzungars are defeated!

0:09:53.440,0:09:54.640
Tell me,

0:09:55.760,0:09:58.054
is your request made for the Great Qing,

0:09:58.880,0:10:00.000
or for her?

0:10:08.640,0:10:10.720
Your Majesty has gone through so much trouble

0:10:10.760,0:10:13.470
just to hear me say this.

0:10:19.400,0:10:22.377
You have always been humble and cautious.

0:10:24.720,0:10:29.449
But when you heard I approved marrying off
 Noble Consort Lumière,

0:10:29.520,0:10:31.036
you recklessly burst into the hall.

0:10:32.280,0:10:37.198
You rarely pay attention to state affairs,

0:10:38.200,0:10:42.579
and you know that I dislike having princes lead the military.

0:10:44.360,0:10:46.283
But for her,

0:10:47.680,0:10:50.828
you request to lead troops against the Dzungars.

0:10:53.280,0:10:56.456
I blame only myself for my blindness,

0:10:57.200,0:10:59.480
not seeing the affair between the two of you!

0:10:59.480,0:11:01.056
Your Majesty is mistaken!

0:11:02.840,0:11:05.417
Had you not recklessly burst into the hall today,

0:11:05.616,0:11:09.430
I would never believe what I was told -

0:11:09.600,0:11:12.003
that you two had met privately outside the palace!

0:11:16.800,0:11:19.070
It was my fault for being oblivious.

0:11:24.000,0:11:26.048
And you....

0:11:27.304,0:11:29.166
Very well!

0:11:29.520,0:11:30.340
Your Majesty!

0:11:31.400,0:11:33.600
Noble Consort Lumière always respectfully
 follows palace protocol.

0:11:34.280,0:11:36.078
I was being reckless.

0:11:36.880,0:11:39.200
Barging into the hall was most inappropriate.

0:11:39.200,0:11:40.720
But I am a son of the Great Qing!

0:11:40.720,0:11:44.577
I cannot bear to see the Great Qing
coerced and humiliated by the Dzungars!

0:11:46.320,0:11:48.320
Although I am incompetent,

0:11:48.320,0:11:52.320
I receive stipends as a Noble Prince
and must devote my entire life to the country!

0:11:54.840,0:11:55.934
Keep going.

0:11:56.520,0:11:59.685
I understand Your Majesty may have presumptions,

0:12:00.920,0:12:04.160
but that's because Your Majesty cares so
 exceedingly for Noble Consort Lumière.

0:12:07.840,0:12:09.811
This is due to Your Noble Highness's merit.

0:12:10.920,0:12:12.475
Over the past years

0:12:12.720,0:12:15.040
I have heard quite a bit of idle talk,

0:12:16.320,0:12:19.087
saying that ever since you married Lord Consort Yuyin,

0:12:19.520,0:12:22.332
you two have been at odds with each other.

0:12:24.440,0:12:27.461
Even Your Majesty is troubled by the affairs in the harem.

0:12:27.840,0:12:32.880
You can surely understand my difficulties
between Yuyin and Jingxian.

0:12:33.320,0:12:37.262
Deep affection gives rise to jealousy, 
and intense jealousy leads to suspicion.

0:12:38.327,0:12:40.800
Disharmony comes from the deepest care.

0:12:42.560,0:12:46.877
In fact, the greatest danger for a couple is suspicion.

0:12:48.040,0:12:50.777
I'm not afraid to endure humiliation
for the sake of the Great Qing.

0:12:51.160,0:12:53.203
But with the previous incident with Dr. Wen,

0:12:53.840,0:12:56.174
and today's matter implicating His Lordship,

0:12:57.000,0:12:59.416
My heart cannot help but feel as cold as ashes.

0:12:59.720,0:13:01.233
Cold as ashes?

0:13:03.600,0:13:07.200
I had a moment of doubt in my mind.

0:13:08.640,0:13:12.957
Yunli married Yuyin because of the cutout paper portrait.

0:13:13.360,0:13:17.003
The portrait did resemble Yuyin.

0:13:17.280,0:13:20.000
But it could also be said to resemble you.

0:13:21.920,0:13:24.110
I don't dare to think further.

0:13:24.920,0:13:26.823
Your Majesty is overthinking.

0:13:29.240,0:13:30.935
I am thinking too much indeed.

0:13:33.360,0:13:38.560
Whether it was Noble Consort Lumière's intention or not,

0:13:39.800,0:13:42.240
her presence created a rift between us brothers

0:13:43.760,0:13:46.254
and attracted covetousness from an outsider.

0:13:46.800,0:13:48.608
She is trouble like "an ominous flood."

0:13:49.440,0:13:52.270
I will grant Galdan's request,

0:13:54.160,0:13:56.090
and send her away from the Great Qing.

0:13:57.720,0:14:00.774
I approve of the marriage alliance with the Dzungars.

0:14:03.400,0:14:04.800
Please reconsider, Your Majesty!

0:14:04.800,0:14:07.188
My mind is made up, and will not be changed.

0:14:15.680,0:14:17.899
"At the spring banquet,"

0:14:18.318,0:14:22.171
"a cup of green wine is raised and a song is sung."

0:14:23.080,0:14:25.279
"I bow and bow to express my three wishes:"

0:14:30.000,0:14:33.600
"May my husband live for a thousand years;"

0:14:39.200,0:14:43.887
"May this humble wife remain ever healthy;"

0:14:49.200,0:14:54.240
"May we be like the returning swallows on the wooden beams,"

0:14:54.240,0:14:56.413
"meeting each other year after year."

0:14:58.480,0:15:01.951
I was a banished concubine.

0:15:03.880,0:15:07.840
Today I can put my meager self to use,
however little, for Your Majesty;

0:15:08.720,0:15:10.479
I will devote myself with no doubts.

0:15:11.640,0:15:16.692
Even though I will not be able to meet Your Majesty year after year,

0:15:17.720,0:15:22.294
I will pray for Your Majesty's longevity and eternal health.

0:15:30.960,0:15:32.183
You may leave now.

0:15:33.040,0:15:33.984
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:15:46.040,0:15:47.535
Let me ask you this:

0:15:48.760,0:15:50.582
You have agreed to the marriage alliance.

0:15:50.582,0:15:52.403
How will you conduct yourself?

0:15:52.920,0:15:54.847
I dare not endure

0:15:55.020,0:15:56.104
any humiliation...

0:15:57.480,0:16:00.113
that would tarnish Your Majesty's reputation.

0:16:03.720,0:16:05.612
I am not Emperor Yuan,

0:16:06.280,0:16:09.393
nor do I want you to be another Zhaojun 
that never returns.

0:16:10.920,0:16:15.306
Even if my seventeenth brother
has any improper intentions toward you,

0:16:16.480,0:16:18.833
I will not truly hold a grudge against him.

0:16:20.160,0:16:23.737
"Love for beauty is only human."

0:16:24.640,0:16:27.470
It is understandable that they covet your beauty.

0:16:28.560,0:16:29.980
However,

0:16:30.625,0:16:33.683
no matter how much others admire your beauty,

0:16:34.280,0:16:38.817
your heart can only belong to me.

0:16:48.807,0:16:51.440
His Majesty issued an edict last night
saying my sister is gravely ill

0:16:51.440,0:16:52.678
and visiting her is forbidden.

0:16:54.240,0:16:56.462
Claiming an illness, and also forbidding visitors -

0:16:57.000,0:16:59.510
this is no different than confining her.

0:17:02.080,0:17:05.563
It seems that His Majesty is intending
to proceed with the marriage alliance.

0:17:06.480,0:17:08.640
As soon as Noble Consort Lumière passes the border,

0:17:09.640,0:17:11.680
His Majesty will announce her death.

0:17:13.200,0:17:17.043
She will be... no more.

0:17:20.816,0:17:23.320
What an inconvenience that we're here in the Summer Palace.

0:17:23.320,0:17:25.160
If your source is reliable,

0:17:25.160,0:17:28.287
we must first return home and then make a careful plan.

0:17:30.496,0:17:32.969
His Majesty will also return to the palace in a day or two.

0:17:35.560,0:17:37.127
Let's go right away.

0:17:45.320,0:17:47.287
I wish I knew how he has been.

0:17:48.280,0:17:51.426
Your Highness still cares about Lord XVII

0:17:51.800,0:17:54.046
even when you are confined and kept in the dark.

0:17:55.280,0:17:57.768
I'm afraid Yunli may lose control of his temper.

0:17:59.600,0:18:01.980
Yesterday, when I bid farewell to His Majesty,

0:18:02.360,0:18:04.991
I was not wishing for His Majesty's longevity,

0:18:05.680,0:18:09.497
but instead hoping Yunli will not lose his composure again, because of me.

0:18:10.760,0:18:12.480
I don't mind what would happen to me,

0:18:12.960,0:18:14.798
but I can't let him be another victim.

0:18:17.120,0:18:18.730
His Majesty...

0:18:19.609,0:18:21.909
is so cruel-hearted.

0:18:23.080,0:18:26.583
"Burnished until the complexion is lustrous as jade,
and sold to the imperial house."

0:18:27.640,0:18:29.920
Even my life is held in His Majesty's hands.

0:18:31.120,0:18:33.083
The supposed "favor and affection"

0:18:33.400,0:18:36.906
cannot compare to the future of the nation and the peace of society.

0:18:37.880,0:18:40.583
Had I asked His Majesty for his pity and protection,

0:18:41.320,0:18:43.108
I would have truly overvalued my worth.

0:18:44.160,0:18:47.750
I see Your Highness... plans to give up on yourself.

0:18:50.120,0:18:51.918
His Majesty already has suspicions.

0:18:53.440,0:18:56.163
Between Yunli and I, one of us cannot be saved.

0:18:57.120,0:19:00.440
Instead of him, I'd rather it be me.

0:19:00.560,0:19:02.694
Your Highness must not have such somber thoughts.

0:19:04.120,0:19:05.343
If he dies,

0:19:06.360,0:19:09.113
no one from his household will be able to survive.

0:19:10.040,0:19:11.374
But if I die,

0:19:12.640,0:19:15.094
His Majesty, in the end, will consider the children

0:19:15.640,0:19:17.423
and will not try to eliminate all of them.

0:19:18.960,0:19:20.639
And what makes you think

0:19:21.120,0:19:24.823
that if he dies, I can continue to live?

0:19:25.040,0:19:26.948
But if misfortune befalls Your Highness,

