0:20:04.320,0:20:05.180
Your Lordship!

0:20:06.080,0:20:07.188
You can't go.

0:20:08.920,0:20:10.000
I have decided.

0:20:12.000,0:20:12.800
Your Lordship,

0:20:13.720,0:20:15.482
His Majesty's suspicions are deeply rooted.

0:20:16.120,0:20:18.056
After so many years of forbearance,

0:20:18.520,0:20:20.880
why risk yourself at this critical juncture?

0:20:22.080,0:20:24.800
You know the reason. No need to ask more.

0:20:27.760,0:20:28.669
Your Lordship,

0:20:30.960,0:20:32.612
do you care so much for Elder Sister

0:20:34.200,0:20:36.119
that you don't care for your own life?

0:20:36.320,0:20:39.390
To protect me, she offered to sacrifice herself.

0:20:40.840,0:20:41.760
I would do the same.

0:20:41.800,0:20:43.200
But she wasn't protecting you!

0:20:43.360,0:20:44.550
She was protecting herself!

0:20:45.280,0:20:47.520
Refusing the marriage alliance would only lead to her death

0:20:47.640,0:20:49.680
while accepting it may give her a chance to live.

0:20:50.455,0:20:52.663
Your Lordship, don't you know how she is?

0:20:54.440,0:20:56.846
Back then, as soon as she heard of your death,

0:20:57.240,0:20:58.560
she returned to the palace.

0:20:59.236,0:21:02.480
Why do you still want to give up your
safety and status for her?

0:21:02.480,0:21:04.338
We both had our difficulties back then.

0:21:05.240,0:21:06.240
Speak no more.

0:21:07.480,0:21:10.320
I never measure actions between Huan'er and myself.

0:21:13.240,0:21:14.320
If anything happens to her,

0:21:14.898,0:21:16.939
I will never forgive myself my entire life.

0:21:18.040,0:21:19.084
Your Lordship!

0:21:20.520,0:21:22.598
I have never begged you for anything.

0:21:23.760,0:21:25.280
This time I am begging you...

0:21:26.440,0:21:28.089
I'm begging you with my life.

0:21:28.680,0:21:30.000
Please don't go.

0:21:31.280,0:21:33.409
She is my elder sister,

0:21:34.280,0:21:36.080
and I am in debt for her kindness,

0:21:37.400,0:21:39.200
but you are my husband

0:21:40.760,0:21:43.442
and the only man I have loved in my life.

0:21:44.840,0:21:47.830
I would rather hurt anyone else

0:21:48.720,0:21:50.695
than allow you to be hurt.

0:21:59.760,0:22:00.760
Yuyin,

0:22:01.880,0:22:03.800
I know I have been unfair to you

0:22:05.320,0:22:07.015
but I can't heed you in this.

0:22:09.440,0:22:12.360
Even if you bring her back,
will His Majesty spare you both?

0:22:13.040,0:22:14.606
Wake up, Your Lordship!

0:22:21.520,0:22:25.440
Since the moment my eyes first beheld her,

0:22:27.320,0:22:29.157
I knew such a day would come.

0:22:31.120,0:22:32.602
Even if I can't save myself,

0:22:34.320,0:22:35.532
I must save her.

0:22:47.760,0:22:48.350
Your Majesty.

0:22:49.920,0:22:51.612
Is everything taken care of?

0:22:53.200,0:22:54.346
Everything is proceeding well.

0:22:54.880,0:22:56.378
The word has been spread.

0:22:56.378,0:23:00.520
Noble Prince Guo will believe that Noble Consort Lumière
has been sent away for the marriage alliance.

0:23:00.600,0:23:01.402
Good.

0:23:03.840,0:23:05.357
No one knows

0:23:06.160,0:23:08.065
that in the wedding sedan,

0:23:08.440,0:23:12.019
lies only the prescription to treat the plague.

0:23:12.880,0:23:14.710
How audacious of Galdan

0:23:15.320,0:23:18.600
to disrespect Heaven's Empire by proposing
marriage to Noble Consort Lumière.

0:23:19.360,0:23:22.141
"Those who accomplish greatness are not bothered by trifles".

0:23:23.160,0:23:26.002
Nor are they fixated on romantic feelings.

0:23:27.240,0:23:31.855
I told him I would only send him the remedy for the plague,

0:23:32.320,0:23:33.750
and he understood this limit.

0:23:33.960,0:23:37.936
But Galdan denied the affair between
Noble Prince Guo and Noble Consort Lumière.

0:23:38.120,0:23:41.748
I was not blind to Galdan's intention to protect her -
driven by his own affection.

0:23:47.200,0:23:52.505
Noble Prince Guo bears the blame.
He dared to covet Your Majesty's woman.

0:23:53.480,0:23:55.137
This is disloyalty to his monarch.

0:23:57.120,0:23:59.580
I know you are good at what you do.

0:24:00.400,0:24:06.121
Now we will see if Yunli pursues 
Noble Consort Lumière to the border.

0:24:07.160,0:24:08.550
If he does,

0:24:10.160,0:24:13.600
that's the proof that he indeed covets my woman.

0:24:15.080,0:24:17.535
I'll have my people watch Noble Consort Lumière

0:24:18.000,0:24:19.748
and make sure no news leaks out.

0:24:21.720,0:24:22.350
Good.

0:24:24.200,0:24:25.655
Galdan has left the capital.

0:24:26.760,0:24:29.760
Announce my decree: we return to the palace tomorrow.

0:24:30.560,0:24:31.369
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:24:36.000,0:24:38.388
Seventeenth brother, leave free of concerns.

0:24:38.640,0:24:41.199
Yurao and I will not give away any information.

0:24:42.360,0:24:44.800
You can cover for me for a while, but not forever.

0:24:46.440,0:24:47.840
You're implicated after all.

0:24:50.000,0:24:52.935
Seventeenth brother, please take good care of yourself.

0:24:56.440,0:25:00.320
Brothers, you are all my personal guards.

0:25:01.080,0:25:03.941
The trip to the frontier is fraught with danger.

0:25:04.600,0:25:06.681
There is a chance that I may not return.

0:25:07.440,0:25:10.974
But still I ask you to aid me with all your strength.

0:25:11.200,0:25:14.218
I am selfish... to put you in this situation.

0:25:14.600,0:25:16.550
We are willing to follow Your Lordship.

0:25:16.880,0:25:20.849
We will disregard life or death
and give our utmost to protect our lord!

0:25:44.480,0:25:45.378
Your Majesty.

0:25:47.080,0:25:48.215
What happened?

0:25:48.520,0:25:50.691
It has been reported that

0:25:50.919,0:25:53.928
Lord XVII has left the capital, leading his mounted guards.

0:26:32.720,0:26:34.000
Peace to Your Majesty.

0:26:34.240,0:26:35.871
Peace to Imperial Father.

0:26:37.080,0:26:38.000
Rise.

0:26:39.480,0:26:41.240
Longyue has grown taller.

0:26:43.080,0:26:46.012
Come here. Let Imperial Father look at you.

0:26:46.240,0:26:47.280
Go.

0:26:51.240,0:26:52.391
What's wrong?

0:26:52.821,0:26:55.480
The princess seems to have some grown-up worries.

0:26:55.480,0:26:58.111
She heard that Hongyan and Lingxi fell ill,

0:26:58.111,0:27:00.000
and kept asking to go and visit them.

0:27:00.000,0:27:03.518
She has been heavyhearted since we returned,
unable to eat or sleep well.

0:27:04.200,0:27:07.343
I visited Lingxi and Hongyan.

0:27:08.320,0:27:13.080
The doctors said their illness was caused
by Spleen-Stomach Disharmony and somber thoughts.

0:27:13.160,0:27:16.386
How can such small children have somber thoughts?

0:27:16.800,0:27:19.302
It must be due to the servants' ineptitude.

0:27:19.920,0:27:22.353
I've already criticized their nursemaids.

0:27:22.920,0:27:26.120
Hongyan and Lingxi haven't seen Mother for a long time.

0:27:26.120,0:27:28.652
They must be missing her terribly.

0:27:28.880,0:27:31.680
I heard Mother has been too sick to get out of bed.

0:27:31.920,0:27:35.120
I cannot comfort my younger brother and sister,

0:27:35.240,0:27:38.071
or care for Mother at her bedside.

0:27:38.320,0:27:40.000
That's why I am sad.

0:27:46.120,0:27:51.928
Estime and the other mothers
treat you well and lovingly.

0:27:52.200,0:27:53.440
I know.

0:27:53.600,0:27:55.560
I was reading Mencius yesterday.

0:27:55.640,0:27:58.520
Mencius said, "The person of virtue has three joys,

0:27:58.520,0:28:01.703
but to rule over a kingdom is not one of them."

0:28:01.703,0:28:05.337
"That his parents are alive and his siblings are at peace; this is one joy."

0:28:05.337,0:28:09.636
"Facing Heaven, he bears no shame; facing his fellow men, he carries no guilt. This is the second joy."

0:28:09.636,0:28:13.324
"Guiding and educating all talented individuals
under Heaven; this is the third joy."

0:28:13.960,0:28:16.000
I hope to become a person of virtue.

0:28:16.000,0:28:18.320
I'll be filial to Imperial Father and my Mother,

0:28:18.520,0:28:20.304
and take good care of my brother and sister.

0:28:42.240,0:28:44.800
Is there anything bothering Your Majesty?

0:28:44.880,0:28:47.000
You haven't been able to sleep well these days.

0:28:47.080,0:28:48.880
Nothing. You should go to sleep.

0:28:52.720,0:28:55.040
Noble Consort Lumière has been convalescing
at the Verdant Reading Hall.

0:28:55.680,0:28:57.680
Since Your Majesty is worried about her,

0:28:57.680,0:29:00.320
why not bring her back to the palace?

0:29:00.440,0:29:04.511
I know Your Majesty cares for Lumière very much.

0:29:05.080,0:29:06.241
Go to sleep.

0:29:34.320,0:29:36.720
Although His Majesty allowed
Your Highness to return to the palace,

0:29:37.240,0:29:41.000
the matter of Lord XVII pursuing Your Highness
 to the border isn't over yet.

0:29:41.120,0:29:44.486
I'm afraid that His Majesty will still
question Your Highness about it.

0:29:45.440,0:29:47.435
Even though he has allowed me back,

0:29:48.319,0:29:51.993
The Palace of Eternal Longevity is empty.
There's not even a ghost here.

0:29:53.640,0:29:56.176
Everyone thinks that I'm still in the Summer Palace.

0:29:57.400,0:29:59.154
If I died now

0:29:59.800,0:30:01.433
would anyone know?

0:30:02.040,0:30:05.000
His Majesty certainly wants to
hear Your Highness's explanation.

0:30:05.280,0:30:09.120
That's why he requested you see him tomorrow 
in the Hall of Mental Cultivation.

0:30:09.520,0:30:11.790
Your Highness should be prepared.

0:30:25.840,0:30:28.350
Your Majesty, Noble Consort Lumière is here.

0:30:44.160,0:30:47.549
Your Majesty, I have recovered from my illness
and come to pay my respects.

0:30:48.080,0:30:50.000
Your illness was not a serious concern.

0:30:51.440,0:30:54.708
But it made Noble Prince Guo believe
you had left for the marriage alliance.

0:30:55.664,0:30:58.332
He led troops to the border without permission.

0:31:02.440,0:31:04.054
Noble Consort Lumière,

0:31:05.941,0:31:08.960
his affection for you is truly deep.

0:31:09.880,0:31:13.400
Your Majesty, I deserve to die ten thousand times
for my ignorance of this.

0:31:13.400,0:31:14.824
You deserve death indeed.

0:31:16.144,0:31:18.867
Do you have anything else to say for yourself?

0:31:19.120,0:31:21.320
Noble Prince Guo left for the border recklessly

0:31:21.320,0:31:23.557
with the intent to protect the Great Qing's dignity.

0:31:23.880,0:31:27.709
However, I was the root of the incident

0:31:28.807,0:31:32.882
I am willing to accept any punishment from Your Majesty.

0:31:33.600,0:31:35.310
Of course I'll punish you.

0:31:35.855,0:31:38.487
I will humbly obey the decree of Heaven.

0:31:38.760,0:31:43.458
It's not just this matter that I want to punish you for.

0:31:45.322,0:31:50.000
But to punish you for several offenses at once,
I don't even know where to start.

0:31:52.375,0:31:54.390
I see you have grown thinner.

0:31:56.120,0:31:59.680
I assume that you continuously
"reflected on yourself facing a wall" in the Summer Palace.

0:32:03.520,0:32:05.510
All right. Su Peisheng.

0:32:06.000,0:32:06.710
Your Majesty.

0:32:07.160,0:32:08.982
Take Noble Consort Lumière back to her palace.

0:32:10.360,0:32:11.062
Yes.

0:32:13.218,0:32:15.064
Go see your children.

0:32:16.104,0:32:19.310
They missed you very much during those days you were ill.

0:32:41.640,0:32:42.780
I take my leave.

0:33:06.840,0:33:08.379
Mother, you have fully recovered.

0:33:09.160,0:33:10.790
Your Highness.

0:33:13.880,0:33:15.610
Go pay respects to your Father.

0:33:16.000,0:33:16.600
Yes.

0:33:30.200,0:33:33.452
Your Majesty, would you like
some almond tea to soothe your throat?

0:33:39.320,0:33:40.254
Su Peisheng.

0:33:40.960,0:33:41.740
Your Majesty.

0:33:42.360,0:33:46.526
Will my forgiveness of Noble Consort Lumière

0:33:47.285,0:33:49.599
make her feel conceited?

0:33:51.880,0:33:55.230
Your Majesty, please forgive me for saying something I shouldn't.

0:33:55.984,0:33:59.024
This matter was not Her Noble Highness's fault.

0:34:05.181,0:34:06.900
It was Yunli's fault.

0:34:08.840,0:34:10.948
He coveted an imperial consort

0:34:11.200,0:34:13.108
and left the capital without permission.

0:34:13.560,0:34:14.756
Rebellion is a treasonous offense.

0:34:14.960,0:34:18.870
Noble Prince Guo wouldn't dare to betray Your Majesty.

0:34:19.720,0:34:21.600
Yunli has already submitted a memorandum,

0:34:21.779,0:34:24.893
admitting the offense of commanding troops
 without permission.

0:34:25.458,0:34:30.000
He requests to guard the border and be punished 
by the hardships of the wind and sand.

0:34:30.720,0:34:33.129
It's just as well if His Lordship does not come back,

0:34:33.200,0:34:35.040
so as not to displease Your Majesty.

0:34:35.240,0:34:36.907
You know nothing!

0:34:37.374,0:34:41.440
If I punish him for this, it will spur idle gossip,

0:34:42.320,0:34:44.734
speculating about the affairs in the palace.

0:34:45.560,0:34:48.790
He asked for punishment, but I'll reward him instead.

0:34:49.920,0:34:51.123
Announce my decree:

0:34:51.280,0:34:55.534
Noble Prince Guo and Venerable Prince Shen
showed their loyalty in defending the country.

0:34:56.000,0:34:58.731
I hereby promote Noble Prince Guo to State Prince Guo,

0:34:58.960,0:35:01.624
and Venerable Prince Shen to Noble Prince Shen.

0:35:02.240,0:35:05.257
State Prince Guo will be stationed outside the Yanming Pass.

0:35:05.257,0:35:10.388
Unless summoned, he cannot return to the capital.

0:35:10.388,0:35:12.099
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:35:16.040,0:35:17.622
[Three years later]

0:35:46.000,0:35:52.157
[“This night brings a full moon and blooming flowers.
May my beloved and I eternally abide in a peaceful life.”]

0:35:53.040,0:35:55.501
Blooming flowers and a full moon are easy to find,

0:35:56.320,0:35:58.914
but a peaceful life with one's beloved cannot last.

0:36:00.720,0:36:03.430
Huan'er, at this moment,

0:36:04.960,0:36:09.301
I hope you are safe and happy under the same moonlight.

0:36:11.360,0:36:13.452
Are these letters reliable?

0:36:14.320,0:36:16.196
Have you confirmed they're not written by someone else?

0:36:16.520,0:36:17.614
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:36:18.040,0:36:20.280
When I paid my respects to Lord Consort Yu,

0:36:20.280,0:36:23.190
I secretly obtained them
from the bottom drawer of her dressing table.

0:36:25.488,0:36:26.720
Are all the letters here?

0:36:26.960,0:36:29.501
I only took these so that they wouldn't notice.

0:36:39.040,0:36:40.602
How's State Prince Guo doing?

0:36:41.160,0:36:44.550
Your Majesty, in the three years State Prince Guo
has guarded the Yanming Pass,

0:36:44.740,0:36:46.928
there has not been a single violation from the Dzungars.

0:36:46.960,0:36:49.630
His Lordship guards the border with rigorous discipline.

0:36:50.120,0:36:52.160
He lives and dines alongside the soldiers

0:36:52.160,0:36:54.652
without growing conceited due to his rank.

0:36:55.188,0:36:58.080
He is obeyed and admired by all the officers and soldiers.

0:36:58.520,0:37:00.538
Is he trying to win their hearts over?

0:37:01.021,0:37:04.956
I presume His Lordship doesn't want to provide
 reasons for criticism.

0:37:05.560,0:37:07.200
I've read his memorandum.

0:37:08.704,0:37:12.112
It quotes a poem that says
"the spring breeze does not blow through the Yumen Pass".

0:37:13.348,0:37:16.079
He emphasized the coldness
and the hardship of the borderlands,

0:37:16.464,0:37:20.000
and asked me to show generosity for the soldiers
and citizens living there.

0:37:20.381,0:37:22.560
He proposed to re-establish mutual trade

0:37:23.258,0:37:26.326
so that the people can enjoy a peaceful and prosperous life.

0:37:27.400,0:37:30.430
His Lordship's suggestions are reasonable.

0:37:30.944,0:37:34.001
Even so, there is no need for him to say more than he should.

0:37:35.415,0:37:39.510
I sent him to guard the border,
not to impose his opinion on state affairs.

0:37:40.400,0:37:42.350
Your Majesty should refrain from anger.

0:37:43.560,0:37:48.958
The imperial doctors advised that anger can counteract
the medicine Your Majesty has been taking.

0:37:54.200,0:37:55.352
It's been three years.

0:38:00.000,0:38:01.750
Summon him back to the capital to report on his work.

0:38:02.560,0:38:03.500
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:38:24.840,0:38:27.209
Mother, look! Dragonflies! Red dragonflies!

0:38:30.120,0:38:32.050
Lingxi, look over there.

0:38:32.360,0:38:34.212
The lotus has bloomed in the lake.

0:38:34.680,0:38:36.590
Why are there lotus flowers in the lake

0:38:36.920,0:38:38.330
but no other flowers?

0:38:39.000,0:38:39.960
It's because...

0:38:40.000,0:38:42.640
The scent of lotus flowers is already refreshing by itself.

0:38:42.720,0:38:45.710
If there were other flowers, it would disrupt the aroma.

0:38:56.760,0:39:00.000
Lingxi, this is your seventeenth uncle.

0:39:00.040,0:39:01.359
Greetings, Seventeenth Uncle.

0:39:03.960,0:39:05.120
Lingxi has grown up so much.

0:39:09.000,0:39:10.890
I heard that Your Lordship was coming back,

0:39:11.600,0:39:13.360
but I didn't expect it to be so soon.

0:39:14.720,0:39:16.360
I haven't returned to the capital for a long time.

0:39:17.000,0:39:21.466
I hurried on the road day and night.
My anxious heart wished to fly as fast as an arrow.

0:39:24.588,0:39:26.795
I haven't seen Your Noble Highness for a long time.

0:39:27.800,0:39:29.360
I trust you have been well.

0:39:29.840,0:39:31.240
Thanks to Your Lordship's blessing,

0:39:31.784,0:39:33.056
all is well.

0:39:39.200,0:39:41.584
Have you seen Yuyin and Yuanchen since you got back?

0:39:42.160,0:39:43.840
I came in a hurry to report to His Majesty.

0:39:43.840,0:39:45.320
I haven't had a chance to go home.

0:39:47.520,0:39:49.751
I will quickly arrange for them to be brought over here.

0:39:50.600,0:39:52.616
The winds and frost are bitter at the borderland.

0:39:53.080,0:39:54.989
Every time Yuyin mentioned it,

0:39:55.760,0:39:57.498
we were all deeply worried for you.

0:39:58.840,0:40:00.453
I thank Your Noble Highness for your concern.

0:40:01.520,0:40:03.615
I have been writing letters to Yuyin all this time

0:40:03.880,0:40:06.720
to lessen her worries and concerns.

0:40:08.400,0:40:09.375
Your Lordship.

0:40:10.760,0:40:13.126
I've finally found you.

0:40:14.080,0:40:15.456
Peace to Your Noble Highness.

0:40:16.520,0:40:17.652
Peace to Your Lordship.

0:40:18.200,0:40:21.280
Your Lordship, His Majesty is expecting you.

0:40:21.280,0:40:23.840
His Majesty has been kept waiting
